          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Considered a luxury, soft-close doors on a Mercedes-Benz GL3 450 are being blamed or a thumb amputation back on October 8, 2021. The victim, Richard J. Kastigar, Jr. who is the chief deputy for the Pima County Sheriff’s Department, has filed a lawsuit for his career-ending injury.",
            "type": "text",
